---
import CtaBlock from './CtaBlock.astro';
---
<section class="section bg-slate-50">
  <div class="section-narrow text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-3">
      Backed By Our 30-Day Unbeatable<br />
      <span class="text-pth-blue">Money-Back Guarantee</span>
    </h2>

    <img src="/images/34-guarantee-refund-detail.png" alt="30-Day Money Back Guarantee — full refund, no questions asked" class="mx-auto my-8 max-w-2xl w-full" />

    <div class="text-left space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Since you've read this far and haven't ordered yet… I'm assuming you're interested but still on the fence.</p>
      <p>Even though these exact tools and systems have been tested with thousands of clients over 20+ years, I get the hesitation.</p>
      <p>So let's take all the risk off of you, and I'll take on all the risk.</p>
      <p><strong>Here's how it works:</strong> Get the course. Practice just ONE technique on yourself or a willing friend or family member.</p>
      <p>And either one of two things will happen.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-pth-green">One — it works.</strong> You witness a real transformation, gain confidence in your abilities, and create an entirely new career path that gives you true purpose.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-pth-red">Or two — it doesn't work.</strong> Then you message our team, and we'll immediately refund you every penny. You'll get to keep the course and all the bonuses.</p>
      <p class="font-semibold text-center text-pth-blue text-xl">So that way, the only possible option is you win.</p>
    </div>

    <CtaBlock />
  </div>
</section>
